Package com.adobe.cq.commerce.pim.api

The API for Product Information Management services for product data stored in CQ.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CatalogBlueprintImporter
    A service to which the ProductDataServlet delegates catalog blueprint importing.
    CatalogGenerator  
    ProductFeedService
    Generates a list of products to be used as a basis for a product feed in various formats (Search&Promote, Target Recommendations etc.).
    ProductImporter
    A service to which the ProductDataServlet delegates product importing.
    ProductInfoManager
    The ProductInfoManager contains administration functions for the management and editing of product data.
    ProductListDecorator
    Decorates a list of Product objects with data obtained from other sources
    ProductServicesManager
